### ==========================================
### 1. AUTH MODULE
### ==========================================

### User Registration
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "name": "John Doe"
}

###

### User Login (Copy the returned token into @authToken above)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}



### ==========================================
### 2. PRODUCTS MODULE
### ==========================================

### Fetch All Products (Default Pagination: page=1, limit=10)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Fetch Products with Custom Pagination & Search
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=1&limit=5&search=chair
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Single Product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/cmrj1t7wj000djiv4rmz51qtr
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Create a New Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Wireless Mechanical Keyboard",
  "description": "RGB Backlit keychron keyboard",
  "price": 89.99,
  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/keyboard.jpg"
}


### ==========================================
### 3. LIKES MODULE
### ==========================================

### Toggle Like on a Product (Like / Unlike)
POST {{baseUrl}}/likes/products/cmrj1t7wj000djiv4rmz51qtr
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get Total Likes Count for a Product (Public/Protected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/likes/products/cmrj1t7wj000djiv4rmz51qtr/count
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}


### ==========================================
### 4. BOOKMARKS MODULE
### ==========================================

### Toggle Bookmark on a Product (Save / Unsave)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bookmarks/products/cm123prodid456
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Get All Bookmarked Products for Current Authenticated User
GET {{baseUrl}}/bookmarks
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}